<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>FuchuGomiSticker</title>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= csp_meta_tag %>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <%= javascript_pack_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
  </head>
  <header>
    <nav class="navbar is-light" role="navigation">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="navbar-start">
          <div class="navbar-brand">
            <%= link_to root_path do %>
              <div class="is-size-2 has-text-weight-bold">
                fuchu-sodai-sticker
              </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="navbar-end">
          <div class="navbar-item">
            <div class="buttons">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>
  </header>
  <body>
  <div class="container">
    <%= yield %>
  </div>
  </body>
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="content">
      <p>
        <strong>東京都府中市 粗大ゴミの料金検索</strong> by junara
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://github.com/junara/fuchu_gomi_sticker">github fuchu_gomi_sticker</a>.
        </li>
        <li>
          粗大ゴミ料金表のデータは<a href="https://www.city.fuchu.tokyo.jp/kurashi/gomirisaikuru/dashikata/sodaigomidasikata.html">東京都府中市のオープンデータ</a>を使っています。
        </li>
      </ul>
      </p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</html>
